<p>
&nbspISS working in two mandals Geesugonda, Narsampet and urban slums of municipal corporation. Registered PLHAS referred to MGM&nbsp Hospital for check up their health conditions. Every month who are eligible essential needed we have been referring all PLHAs for CD4&nbsp Count test and other related tests. (T.B,) in MGM Hospital. and community care centers.<br>
