</p>
<p>
<h5>&nbspCancer & T.B. Awareness Programs</h5>
&nbspDuring 2009-2010 ISS conducted sensitization program to educate them regarding the serious effects of smoking and alcoholism. Due to the above bad habits, people are subjected to chronic diseases like T.B, Cancer etc. During these programmes Dr. Mohan Rao and other doctors have clearly explained as to how the use of Gutkas, Zardas leads to heart diseases. Similarly it was also explained as to how breast cancer takes place in women and the preventive measures to be taken.
ISS identified some cases and referred to Cancer Hospitals and DOT Centers.
</p>
